{"tid":526003,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手求助] i7 7700溫度問題","createTime":"2018-01-11T09:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T15:47:28.000Z","uid":79372,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa3beec2433e4eff9a4897441958d2f1ab4fbc0","tid":526003,"uid":79372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"求大佬們幫幫眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，小弟啱啱新換咗粒u同mb，打pubg發現cpu溫度好鬼高，琴晚打咗成晚pubg+開discord，多數時間係80-90度，最高試過衝上95-100，但唔睇溫度嘅話全程冇咩特別不良狀況。<br />\n於是我今日測試咗陣，啱啱開機溫度會係35-40，開youtube睇咗一個鐘1080p就40-50，開pubg最高graphic打咗45分鐘，in game 溫度初期會喺70-80，慢慢會升到80~90，喺lobby都有70，quit game返desktop待機會變返60。請問呢個情況係咪唔正常？<br />\n<br />\nspec：<br />\ncpu: i7 7700 3.6GHz<br />\nmb: gigabyte intel B250<br />\ncase: cooler master elite 382 usb3.0 atx<br />\n散熱：enermax water cooler<br />\ngpu: gtx 1080<br />\nos: win10 x64"},{"pid":"194ff5cc286a1fb7f89e94bf23d456733a262e9d","tid":526003,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"我1080ti cpu一樣<br />\n用原裝散熱都係60-70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a7578c9ac706d029d6731b353f308e265d394c","tid":526003,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"cpu cooler裝好未? 試下拆落嚟重新落過散熱膏再裝多次"},{"pid":"b6efd21c8c084d20cdaa7fae6c2e3ae9ccf37de6","tid":526003,"uid":79372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8a7578c9ac706d029d6731b353f308e265d394c","tid":526003,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"cpu cooler裝好未? 試下拆落嚟重新落過散熱膏再裝多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"cooler照計就有裝好"},{"pid":"036c3de2429fe562fb6e49624f6a11ddc82ffac6","tid":526003,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"粒cpu喺邊度買？"},{"pid":"ba024bfb7c483ba54931f52363f9b48993852b9a","tid":526003,"uid":116497,"like":